LXI H, 2000H ; Load memory address of dividend (2000H) into HL
LXI D, 2001H ; Load memory address of divisor (2001H) into DE
MVI A, 00H ; Clear accumulator to store quotient
MVI B, 08H ; Initialize counter to 8
LOOP;
DAD H ; Shift dividend left
SUB M ; Subtract divisor from dividend
JNC NOADD ; Jump if result is positive or zero
ADD M ; Restore dividend if negative
NOADD;
ORA A ; Set quotient bit
RLC ; Shift quotient left
DCR B ; Decrement counter
JNZ LOOP ; Repeat if counter is not zero
; Optional; Store the quotient in another register or memory location;
STA 3002H ; Store quotient in memory location 3002H
HLT ; Halt the program
